headline: Realtor.com® October 12-18th Marks the Best Time to Buy a Home in 2025
summary: The best time to buy a home in 2025 is fast approaching. According to the Realtor.com®2025 Best Time to Buy Report, the week of October 12–18 will be the year's sweet spot for home shoppers, with a rare combination of higher inventory (32.6% more active listings from the start of the year), lower prices (a potential savings of $15,000), and less competition (30.6% lower) that makes it advantageous for buyers.
